presentation
============

make clear that the security requirement for x * y is
- y == 0 or x < UINT_MAX / y
or
- x_2n * y_2n <= UINT_MAX

make clear that 1 << n never yields 0 because
1) 1 << n != 0 if n < 32
2) undefined   if n >= 32
